<section class="section-body directions">
  <h1 class="section-title getting-here">Getting Here</h1>
  <div class="mobile-directions">
    <h2>By Plane</h2>
    <h4>Fly into Zürich Airport</h5>
    <h2>By Train</h2>
    <h4>Take a SBB Train to Interlaken, transfer trains to a Lauterbrunnen bound train.
        You can take the cable car from Wengen to Männlichen, or the gondola from Grindelwald Grund to
        Männlichen. Wengen and Grindelwald Grund can be reached by train.</h4>
